quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  70,1,"Soakd n soke, naon-yɩtg yelle."
  70,2,"Kɩfr-dãmbã zugu a pa tar tusd ye."
  70,3,"N yaa Wẽnd nengẽ sẽn yaa rʋʋb zĩig Soabã."
  70,4,"Malεgsã la a Gibriila rʋʋda Yẽ nengẽ raar pʋgẽ t'a makr yaa yʋʋm tus pis-nu."
  70,5,"Bɩ f maan sugr sẽn be neere."
  70,6,"Ad bãmb ne-a lame t'a zãra."
  70,7,"Tɩ Tõnd yaool n ne-a t'a pẽ."
  70,8,"Raar ning saagã sẽn na n lebg wala kũud sẽn yẽnege."
  70,9,"Tɩ tãmsã lebg wala kõbdo."
  70,10,"Pa yã-to-kõn-n-gũs pa sokd a noang-n-taag yell ye."
  70,11,"B yãta taaba, nin-wẽng noangame t'a sã n da tõe n rɩk ɑ koɑmbɑ n yao n yi ra-kãngã naongã."
  70,12,"La a pag la a ma-biiga."
  70,13,"La a rog-pẽtb nins yẽ sẽn ra relldã."
  70,14,"La sẽn be Tẽng zug gilli, rẽ poorẽ tɩ b tɩlg yẽnda."
  70,15,"Pa woto ye! Ad yaa Laẓaa pugum."
  70,16,"Sẽn yaa zu-gãnd tõosda."
  70,17,"N boond ned ning sẽn gõd a kuidg n daeegdẽ."
  70,18,"La a tigim ɑrzεkã n sui."
  70,19,"B naana ninsaalã t'a yaa tibda."
  70,20,"Wẽng sã n paam-a a pɑ tɑr sugr suu."
  70,21,"La sõma sã n paam-a a yaa sẽn gɩdgde."
  70,22,"Ralla pʋʋsdbã,"
  70,23,"Neb nins tɩ b pʋʋsgã zugu, b yaa ruumdba."
  70,24,"La neb ninsi, tɩ be bãmb arzεkã pʋgẽ, hakε b sẽn mi."
  70,25,"N kõt bõosɑ, la b sẽn mong-a soabɑ."
  70,26,"La neb nins sẽn kõt-b sɩd ne Samã Rolb Raarã."
  70,27,"La neb nins sẽn yaa yɑeesdbɑ ne b Soabã naongã."
  70,28,"Ad bãmb Soabã naongã pa tar bas-m-yam ye."
  70,29,"Bãmb la sẽn gũusd b taoã ( n yit yoobo)."
  70,30,"Ralla b pagbẽ ma b yemb-pogsẽ, ad zĩ-kãngã, b pa sãbs-b ye."
  70,31,"La ned ning sẽn bao woto loogr poorẽ, ad bãmb rãmb la maan-n-zʋʋg rãmba."
  70,32,"La neb nins tɩ bãmb boablã pʋgẽ la b pʋlengã, b yaa gũudba."
  70,33,"La neb nins sẽn yãs tɩrg ne b kaset-rãmba."
  70,34,"La neb nins tɩ b Pʋʋsgã, b gũusdame."
  70,35,"Bãmbã rãmba, b bee Arzãn-rãmb pʋsẽ tɩ b waoogd-ba."
  70,36,"Lɑ yɑɑ bõe n tar sẽn kɩfl-bã tɩ b zoet n gondedg fo wεεngẽ."
  70,37,"Rɩtg wεεngẽ la goabg wεεngẽ sull-sulli."
  70,38,"Ned fãa tẽeda bãmb pʋgẽ t'a na n kẽe arzãn sẽn yaa neema wã."
  70,39,"Pa woto ye! Tõnd naana bãmb ne bũmb ning bãmb sẽn mi wã."
  70,40,"M na wẽen ne wĩntoog sẽn pugsdẽ Soabã, la wĩntoog sẽn lʋɩtẽ Soabã, ad Tõnd yaa Tõogda."
  70,41,"Ne D tedg sõma sẽn yɩɩd bãmbɑ, la Tõnd pa yɩ b sẽn na n põsg-b rãmb ye."
  70,42,"Bɩ f bas-b tɩ b faood la b reemdẽ hal n wa seg raar ning b sẽn pʋlem-bã."
  70,43,"Raar ning bãmb sẽn yit b yaadẽ wã n yãgdẽ tɩ yaa wala bãmb fõodame n dengd tɑɑbɑ n tʋgd kug sẽn tilgi."
  70,44,"B nin yaa sẽn nodge, tɩ yaalg buiid-ba; rẽ la raar ning b sẽn da pʋlem bãmbã."
